103
00:10:43,830 --> 00:10:44,630
Why don't we

104
00:10:45,100 --> 00:10:47,690
take his pretty belt

105
00:10:47,900 --> 00:10:49,590
and leave him run his course?

106
00:11:11,450 --> 00:11:21,250
[Soul Land]

107
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:25,330
Brother.

108
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,660
Even though we live on Purple Pearl Island,

109
00:11:28,130 --> 00:11:29,260
we're not pirates.

110
00:11:29,530 --> 00:11:30,860
We can't harm human life.

111
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:32,930
If the Purple Pearl Pirates make trouble,

112
00:11:33,500 --> 00:11:35,030
