117
00:11:40,800 --> 00:11:42,290
Don't let them find you.

118
00:11:42,830 --> 00:11:43,860
Okay, got it.

119
00:11:58,600 --> 00:11:59,160
You're awake?

120
00:12:00,500 --> 00:12:01,290
Who are you?

121
00:12:02,130 --> 00:12:03,490
Why am I here?

122
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:06,190
My name is Ji Xiang.

123
00:12:06,500 --> 00:12:08,760
I am the only doctor on Purple Pearl Island.

124
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,430
I found you

125
00:12:10,430 --> 00:12:11,990
passed out on the beach yesterday,

126
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,090
so I brought you back here.

127
00:12:13,500 --> 00:12:16,360
As for what happened before that,
do you not remember?

128
00:12:18,430 --> 00:12:19,430
My friends and I

129
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:22,990
were attacked by the Purple Pearl Pirates.

130
00:12:23,300 --> 00:12:24,630
Even though I'm alive,

131
00:12:25,060 --> 00:12:27,060
I don't know if the others still are.

132
00:12:29,630 --> 00:12:31,890
Even though I don't know what happened to you,

133
00:12:32,460 --> 00:12:34,790
not all pirates are bad.

134
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:36,660
Besides, good people are blessed.

135
00:12:37,300 --> 00:12:38,630
I believe that your friends

136
00:12:38,630 --> 00:12:39,660
are still alive too.

137
00:12:42,730 --> 00:12:43,330
Maybe

138
00:12:44,030 --> 00:12:45,430
what you say is true.

139
00:12:46,300 --> 00:12:47,130
No matter what,

140
00:12:47,530 --> 00:12:48,390
thank you for saving me.

141
00:12:48,930 --> 00:12:50,060
I owe you my life.

142
00:12:51,560 --> 00:12:52,160
Alright.

143
00:12:53,330 --> 00:12:54,230
Get some rest first.

144
00:13:24,800 --> 00:13:25,630
Who knew that

145
00:13:25,860 --> 00:13:27,960
after absorbing power from the
Magic Whale King of the Deep Sea,

146
00:13:28,460 --> 00:13:30,360
the Eight Spider Bone evolved again.

147
00:13:31,330 --> 00:13:33,990
But I've engulfed the power too much.

148
00:13:34,400 --> 00:13:36,460
It's creating a huge burden for my body.

149
00:13:37,630 --> 00:13:40,030
I need to quickly finish absorbing it
and go find the others.

150
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:16,330
Even the strongest ocean soul beasts

151
00:14:16,760 --> 00:14:19,460
