154
00:14:27,460 --> 00:14:28,290
Help,

155
00:14:28,360 --> 00:14:29,390
Doctor Ji Xiang!

156
00:14:55,500 --> 00:14:56,290
Doctor Ji Xiang!

157
00:14:56,460 --> 00:14:57,560
Please save my brother.

158
00:14:58,300 --> 00:14:59,060
